The actress took to Instagram on Tuesday to share a clip of her teary-eyed self in a taxi. She said the taxi had to be stopped while pictures of her were being taken by passengers and the driver.She revealed that the experience reminded her of a time when she couldn't even afford taxi fare."It's been years since this was my life... that one trip took me back to days when I didn't even have taxi fare, now the entire taxi stopped to take pictures with me, including the driver," she wrote alongside the video."In our lifetime everything is possible," she added.Watch Zikhona's taxi experience on the clip below:A video posted by Zikhona Sodlaka (@zikhonasodlaka) on Oct 18, 2016 at 8:40am PDT Find the hottest celebrity and entertainment news on TshisaLIVE or follow TshisaLIVE on Facebook and Twitter.